            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/vehicles",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "vehicles"]
            },
            "description": "Create a new vehicle.\n\n**Required role:** ADMIN\n**vehicleType values:** CAR, MOTORCYCLE, TRUCK, VAN, BUS, SUV\n**registrationNumber:** uppercase letters, digits, hyphens only (e.g. ABC-1234)\n\nThe vehicleId variable is auto-set from the response for use in other requests."
